          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Protect Local Independence in Housing Act of 2015</b></p> <p>Amends the Fair Housing Act to prohibit its provisions from being construed to prohibit conduct resulting in a disparate impact on a class protected by such Act unless the person engaging in that conduct intended that impact.</p>]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <updateDate>2015-07-21T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
